  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Nal smiles when she sees you. \u201cI've spent more time speaking with\nthe Verdessian plant you and I found at the market,\" she says. \"You'll\nbe happy to know that I can hear the spirit of the Verdessa again,\nthough only faintly. She's distracted and worried about something."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"The spirit of the Valley is agitated as well. Be careful out there. Don't\nbe shy about asking the ancestors for assistance.\""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"Speaking of which,\" she says. \"Would you like to assist me by\naccompanying me to the market again?\""
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "em",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Clear Nal with"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "type": "icon",
                      "icon": "progress",
                      "color": "black"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "to discuss another trip to Kobo's Market."
                }
              ],
              "color": "blue"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
